	<string>Secure Proton Pass Alfred workflow.

Requirements:
- pass-cli (brew install protonpass/tap/pass-cli)
- terminal-notifier (brew install terminal-notifier) — optional
- Python 3 (macOS built-in)

Usage:
- Type 'pp' to search your vault
- Enter: Copy password (auto-clears after 30s)
- Cmd+Enter: Copy username
- Alt+Enter: Copy TOTP (auto-clears after 30s)
- Shift+Enter: Open URL in browser

No secrets on disk. No shell injection.</string>
